com.gsma.mobileconnect.r2
Class MobileConnectStatus

java.lang.Object
  com.gsma.mobileconnect.r2.MobileConnectStatus

public class MobileConnectStatus
extends java.lang.Object

Object to hold the details of a response returned from @see MobileConnectInterface and MobileConnectWebInterface all information required to continue the process is included

Since:
2.0

Returns:
MobileConnectStatus with MobileConnectStatus.ResponseType.START_AUTHENTICATION

startDiscovery

public static MobileConnectStatus startDiscovery()
Creates a Status with ResponseType#START_DISCOVERY. Indicates that some required data was missing and the discovery process needs to be restarted.

Returns:
MobileConnectStatus with MobileConnectStatus.ResponseType.START_DISCOVERY

authentication

public static MobileConnectStatus authentication(java.lang.String url,
                                                 java.lang.String state,
                                                 java.lang.String nonce)
Creates a Status with ResponseType#AUTHENTICATION and url for next process step. Indicates that the next step should be navigating to the Authorization URL.

Parameters:
url - Url returned from IAuthenticationService
state - The unique state string generated or passed in for the authorization url
nonce - The unique nonce string generated or passed in for the authorization url
Returns:
MobileConnectStatus with MobileConnectStatus.ResponseType.AUTHENTICATION

complete

response - RequestTokenResponse returned from IAuthenticationService
Returns:
MobileConnectStatus with MobileConnectStatus.ResponseType.COMPLETE

the instance of MobileConnectStatus
